snippet.title: The Sims 3 Into the Future: Producer Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Discover the future and the world of Oasis Landing!

Get The Sims 3 Into The Future here: http://bit.ly/FutureSims3

Discover the future and everything that Oasis Landing has to offer in the upcoming The Sims 3 Into The Future expansion pack! Conquer all-new future technology, create customizable Plumbots, and maybe even instigate an alternative future world! Take your Sims to the future and back! Available October 22, 2013.
